  "title": "Consumer Protection - As introduced, enacts \"The Tennessee Safe Stores and Staffed Stores Act;\" requires drug and food retail establishments using self-service checkout stations to maintain a minimum staffing ratio, limits self-service transactions to no more than 15 items, and prohibits the purchase of age-restricted or security-tagged merchandise at self-service checkout stations. - Amends TCA Title 47, Chapter 18 and Title 50.",
